                    "subtype": "ability",
                    "name": "Starting Drop",
                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "text": "The only way to launch a Hillcross glider is to jump off a steep incline with favorable wind conditions. The glider is uncontrolled and falls 60 feet each round until the pilot successfully Takes Control . If the glider hits the ground before the pilot Takes Control, the pilot and the glider both take falling damage.",
